article.description: — Felipe Haase recorded 14 points and 12 rebounds to lead Mercer to a 71-64 win over The Citadel on Monday night.
article.headline: Haase carries Mercer past The Citadel 71-64
article.linkText: Haase carries Mercer past The Citadel 71-64
article.story: CHARLESTON, S.C. -- — Felipe Haase recorded 14 points and 12 rebounds to lead Mercer to a 71-64 win over The Citadel on Monday night. James Glisson III had 16 points and nine rebounds for Mercer (11-7, 4-1 Southern Conference). Jordan Jones added 10 points. Jalen Johnson had five blocks. Stephen Clark had 18 points, nine rebounds and five blocks for the Bulldogs (7-9, 1-4). Hayden Brown added 16 points and eight rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
